00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,590
The great rose of Sharon

851
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:52,330
♫Grew in the northwest♫

852
00:37:52,430 --> 00:37:52,990
grew in the northwest,

853
00:37:53,210 --> 00:37:54,350
♫Lived on miasma♫

