00:37:54,350 --> 00:37:55,070
lived on miasma.

855
00:37:57,710 --> 00:37:58,630
It grew by rivers

856
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:00,510
and flourished to the River Gu.

857
00:38:02,630 --> 00:38:03,190
What does it mean?

